widgets_values: EasyCache can speed up this workflow, but it will also sacrifice the video quality. If you need it, use Ctrl+B to enable.
Split at matching sigma to the noise scale
Use the VAE Decode (Tiled) if it takes too long to get the final video.
If you don't have enough VRAM and encounter the OOM error, please try to set the `weight_dtype` to `fp8_e4n3fn`.

widgets_values: A paper airplane released from the top of a skyscraper, gliding through urban canyons, crossing traffic, flying over streets, spiraling upward between buildings. The camera follows the paper airplane's perspective, shooting cityscape in first-person POV, finally flying toward the sunset, disappearing in golden light. Creative camera movement, free perspective, dreamlike colors.

nodes.title: 说明
widgets_values:
# 【玩法说明】 
---
## 这个开关，跑提升1080p时，打开“yes”

镜头缓慢推进，聚焦人物面部特写。自然光从斜上方洒落，光影在脸颊与鼻梁间流动，随人物轻微转动头部而微妙变化。环绕头部的蔷薇与白色小花轻轻颤动，花瓣被风掀起，轻触眼睑与发梢，带来朦胧梦幻的互动感。人物微卷长发随风飘扬，发丝与花茎缠绕、分离，形成动态交织。背景轻微虚化，阳光透过花瓣与发丝洒下斑驳光点，整体色调温暖柔和，呈现细腻胶片质感。人物眼神微动，嘴角轻扬，仿佛回应风中花语，动作自然流畅，充满诗意与生命力.
